{"msg":"返回成功","muban":[{"ename":"ay","cunt":25,"grade":"1.0","cname":"A1型题","shiti":[{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"婴幼儿，4个月，早期萌芽，萌了几颗牙齿","discription":"本题考查体格生长常用指标及测量方法。牙齿：人出生后4～10个月乳牙开始萌出，12个月未萌出者为乳牙萌出延迟。约于2岁半乳牙出齐。2岁内乳牙数目为月龄减4～6。6岁左右萌出第l颗恒磨牙，12岁萌出第2颗恒磨牙，17～18岁萌出第3颗恒磨牙(智齿)。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0004_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"4颗","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"6颗","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"10颗","fourth":"8颗","answerPic":"","first":"2颗"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"门脉高压患者出血的特点是","discription":"在门静脉压增高的的状态下，常发生典型的病理生理变化之一是静脉交通支扩张，突出改变是此处门一腔静脉交通支扩张，以食底下段及胃底交通支最为重要，食底下段及胃底曲张静脉突然破裂发生急性大出血，患者会呕吐鲜红色血液或排出柏油样便，甚至很快形成休克；由于肝功能损害至凝血功能障碍，脾功能亢进致血小板减少，因此出血常不易自止。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0012_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"以便血为主，可自行停止","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"有呕血、便血、可自行停止","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"出血量小，可自行停止","fourth":"有呕血、便血、不能自行停止","answerPic":"","first":"以呕血为主，可自行停止"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者女，40岁。孕2产2，行子宫肌瘤切除术后1天。此时应为患者采取的体位是","discription":"半坐位的适用范围：(1)某些面部及颈部手术后，减少局部出血。(2)胸腔疾病、胸部创伤或心脏疾病引起呼吸困难的患者，采取半坐位由于重力原因，部分血液留滞下肢和盆腔，回心血量减少，从而减轻肺淤血和心脏负担；同时使膈肌下降，减少腹腔内脏器对心肺的压力，肺活量增加，有利于气体交换，使呼吸困难的症状得到改善。(3)腹腔、盆腔手术后或者有炎症的患者，采取半坐位可使腹腔渗出液流入盆腔，促使感染局限，便于引流。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0016_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"右侧卧位","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"去枕平卧位","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"左侧卧位","fourth":"半坐卧位","answerPic":"","first":"中凹位"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"1岁女婴，出生史正常，喂养正常。现进行常规生长发育检查。该女婴的左手腕部X线摄片，可显示的骨化中心数量最多为","discription":"本题考查儿童生长发育中长骨的发育。1～9岁腕骨骨化中心数目约其岁数+1，故选B。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0032_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"2个","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"0个","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"8个","fourth":"6个","answerPic":"","first":"4个"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"诊断急性呼吸窘迫综合征的必要条件是","discription":"内科急性呼吸窘迫综合征中，动脉血气分析中PaO<sub>2</sub>/FiO<sub>2</sub>是常使用指标，是诊断ALI(急性肺损伤)和ARDS(急性呼吸窘迫综合征)的必要条件，正常值是400～500，ALI时≤300，ARDS时≤200。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0034_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"PaO<sub>2</sub>／FiO<sub>2</sub>＜200","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"PaO<sub>2</sub>／FiO<sub>2</sub>＜300","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"PaCO<sub>2</sub>／FiO<sub>2</sub>＜300","fourth":"PaCO<sub>2</sub>／FiO<sub>2</sub>＜200","answerPic":"","first":"PWCP＜18mmHg"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者男，38岁，因急腹症手术治疗，术中见腹腔少量淡黄色腹水，有粪臭味，考虑其致病菌为","discription":"本题考查急性化脓性腹膜炎。腹膜炎主要致病菌是胃肠道内常驻菌群，其中以大肠埃希菌最多见，其次是厌氧菌、链球菌、变形杆菌等。本题患者腹内有渗出液颜色呈黄绿色，考虑大肠埃希菌，一般常与其他致病菌混合感染而变得稠厚、并有粪臭味。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0045_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"大肠杆菌","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"变形杆菌","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"溶血性链球菌","fourth":"绿脓杆菌","answerPic":"","first":"金黄色葡萄球菌"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"带教老师在临床带教过程中为了给实习护士创造机会，有合适的静脉穿刺对象时就对患者说：“她虽然是个学生，但穿刺技术非常熟练，××都是她穿刺的，而且每次都能成功，您能给她一次穿刺的机会吗?”在此护患沟通的过程中，带教老师使用的是","discription":"带教老师跟患者说“××是她穿刺成功的”暗示同学技术不错。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0060_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"安慰性语言","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"指令性语言","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"积极的暗示语言","fourth":"鼓励性语言","answerPic":"","first":"劝说性语言"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者男，40岁，风湿性心脏病二尖瓣狭窄，住院期间护士遵医嘱给予患者心电监护，患者最易出现的是","discription":"风湿性心脏病二尖瓣狭窄并发症：(1)心房颤动，是相对早期常见并发症；(2)右心衰，晚期常见并发症；(3)急性肺水肿；(4)血栓栓塞；(5)肺部感染；(6)感染性心内膜炎，较少见。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0062_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"二度2型房室传导阻滞","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"预激综合征","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"心房颤动","fourth":"室性阵发性心动过速","answerPic":"","first":"室性期前收缩"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"最易发生骨折的肋骨是","discription":"本题考查肋骨骨折患者护理。肋骨骨折多数是外来暴力所致，可分为直接暴力和间接暴力，以第4～7肋骨折最为常见。记忆性内容。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0064_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"C","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"第7～10肋","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"第4～7肋","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"第1～3肋","fourth":"第4～5肋","answerPic":"","first":"第11～12肋"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者男，50岁，在建筑工地干活时被一铁钉扎伤，医嘱予以破伤风肌内注射，护士在给患者皮试时","discription":"B实验结果为阳性时，才做破伤风脱敏试验；破伤风皮试液的浓度是150IU／ml；实验结果为阴性时，剩余剂量做肌内注射；皮试结果阳性鉴定是皮丘直径大于1．5cm时，红晕超过4cm。有时皮丘周围有伪足，痒感。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0071_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"实验结果为阴性时，可做破伤风脱敏试验","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"破伤风皮试液的浓度是1500IU／ml","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"当皮丘周围有伪足，痒感时可以判断为阳性","fourth":"实验结果为阴性时，余液0．9ml与皮试剩余剂量做肌内注射","answerPic":"","first":"当皮丘直径大于1．5cm时，红晕超过4cm可以判断为结果阳性"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者女，72岁。因脑梗死入院治疗，护理为其口腔护理前，发现有义齿，取下后应该放置于下列哪种杯子里","discription":"本题考查患者的清洁护理。义齿放置于冷开水中，不可放在乙醇中或热水中。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0074_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"盛有75％酒精的杯子里","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"干燥的杯子里","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"盛有冷水的杯子里","fourth":"盛有热水的杯子里","answerPic":"","first":"盛有30％酒精的杯子里"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"护士与患者家属沟通过程，错误的是","discription":"选项A、B、C、D均是正确的，参与治疗不是护士与患者家属沟通的内容，故选E。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0084_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"给予患者家属心理支持","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"指导患者家属对患者进行生活照顾","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"指导患者家属参与患者的治疗过程","fourth":"指导患者家属参与患者的护理过程","answerPic":"","first":"尊重患者"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"下列患者资料中属于主观资料的是","discription":"(1)主观资料：即患者的主诉，包括患者所感觉的、所经历的以及看到的、听到的、想到的内容的描述，是通过与患者及有关人员交谈获得的资料，也包括亲属的代诉，如头晕、麻木、乏力、瘙瘁、恶心、疼痛等。(2)客观资料：是护士经观察、体检、借助其他仪器检查或实验室检查等所获得的患者的健康资料，如黄疸、发绀、呼吸困难、颈项强直、心脏杂音、体温39．0℃等。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0094_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"头晕、麻木、乏力","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"体温39℃","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"呼吸困难","fourth":"黄疸、发绀","answerPic":"","first":"颈项强直"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者男，33岁，炼钢工人，工作不慎烧伤，Ⅲ度烧伤面积60％，应采用的隔离方法为","discription":"保护性隔离亦称为反向隔离。适用于抵抗力低下或极易感染的患者，如大面积烧伤、早产儿、白血病及脏器移植、免疫缺陷的患者等。主要隔离措施：(1)患者住单人房间。(2)接触患者前须洗手，戴口罩、帽子、换鞋、穿无菌隔离衣；患有呼吸道疾病或咽部带菌者应避免接触患者。(3)病室内空气、家具及地面等严格消毒。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0099_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"严密隔离","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"消化道隔离","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"呼吸道隔离","fourth":"接触隔离","answerPic":"","first":"保护性隔离"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"子宫内膜异位症患者卵巢病变最常见的类型是","discription":"","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0118_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"卵巢黄体囊肿","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"卵巢滤泡囊肿","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"卵巢巧克力囊肿","fourth":"卵巢炎性包块","answerPic":"","first":"卵巢恶性肿瘤"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"ARDS患者最容易出现的心理问题是","discription":"","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0139_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"C","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"焦虑","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"恐惧","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"抑郁","fourth":"绝望","answerPic":"","first":"孤独感"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"腹外疝患者因担心疝块反复突出影响工作和生活，最常产生的主要心理问题是","discription":"","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0149_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"C","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"忧郁","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"焦虑","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"愤怒","fourth":"恐惧","answerPic":"","first":"自卑"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"胸部外伤后出现胸廓软化是由于","discription":"多根多处肋骨骨折会使局部胸壁失去支撑软化，出现反常呼吸运动。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0158_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"胸骨骨折","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"锁骨骨折","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"胸肌大面积损伤","fourth":"多根多段肋骨骨折","answerPic":"","first":"一根肋骨多处骨折"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"目前确诊慢性胃炎最可靠的方法是","discription":"胃镜检查是确诊慢性胃炎最可靠的确诊方法。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0165_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"血清抗体测定","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"胃肠钡餐检查","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"幽门螺杆菌检测","fourth":"纤维胃镜检查","answerPic":"","first":"胃液分析"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者女，45岁，患类风湿关节炎，自诉最近晨僵较严重，下列缓解晨僵的护理措施正确的是","discription":"缓解晨僵的护理措施：(1)活动期发热或关节肿胀明显时应卧床休息，并保持正确的体位勿长时间维持抬高头部和膝部的姿势，以免屈曲姿势造成关节挛缩致残。(2)病情缓解时指导患者进行功能锻炼。可做关节的被动活动，也可训练日常生活技能，如穿脱衣服、进食、如厕等保持生活自理能力。锻炼过程中应注意运动量要适当，循序渐进，不可操之过急，运动前可用热敷、热水浴、红外线等理疗方法改善血液循环，缓解肌肉挛缩。(3)当病变发展至关节强直时，应保持关节的功能位置，必要时用夹板固定，以保持一定的生活自理能力。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0179_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"夜间睡眠时戴弹力手套保暖","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"尽量不要活动僵硬的关节","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"禁用止痛药","fourth":"关节内可注射透明质酸","answerPic":"","first":"早晨起床后先用冷水浸泡僵硬关节然后按摩"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"胆道蛔虫病患者临床表现最重要的特点是","discription":"本病的特点是剧烈的腹部绞痛与不相称的轻微腹部体征，即症状与体征不符。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0181_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"B","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"症状与体征不符","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"症状可自行缓解","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"疼痛呈反复、间歇发作","fourth":"多不伴黄疸","answerPic":"","first":"发作时伴恶心、呕吐"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患儿女，2岁，出生时青紫，初步诊断为法洛四联症，近日家长带小儿就诊，准备手术，下列护理措施错误的是","discription":"休息是恢复心脏功能的重要条件。休息可减少组织对氧的需要，减少心脏负担，使症状缓解。所以应安排好患儿的作息时间，保证休息和睡眠，根据病情安排适当活动量，以免加重心脏负荷。重症患儿，应绝对卧床休息，给予生活照顾，集中护理，并减少不必要的刺激，避免引起情绪激动和哭闹。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0183_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"预防感染","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"保证睡眠与休息","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"吸氧","fourth":"增加活动量","answerPic":"","first":"进一步诊断检查"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者女，40岁，行胆总管切开取石T管引流术后5天，T管引流液每天2000ml，提示","discription":"T管引流护理：观察记录胆汁的量及性状：胆汁引流一般每天约300～700ml。量过少可能因“T”形管阻塞或肝功能衰竭所致；量多可能是胆总管下端不够通畅。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0188_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"胆汁量正常","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"胆汁量偏少","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"肝总管梗阻","fourth":"肠液反流","answerPic":"","first":"胆总管下段梗阻"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者男，37岁，突发剧烈头痛5小时伴呕吐，体温36．7℃，脉搏76次／分，血压120／74mmHg，呼吸20次／分，颈项强直抵抗，kerning征阳性，诊断为蛛网膜下腔出血，该患者的护理问题不包括","discription":"根据案例患者不存在体液过多的诊断，反而因为呕吐会丢失大量体液存在体液不足的诊断。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0195_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"舒适的改变，头痛","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"焦虑、恐惧","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"知识缺乏","fourth":"潜在并发症：再次出血","answerPic":"","first":"体液过多"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"乙脑病毒主要侵犯的人体系统是","discription":"流行性乙型脑炎简称乙脑，是由乙型脑炎病毒引起的，以脑实质炎症为主要的中枢神经系统急性传染病。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0202_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"E","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"呼吸系统","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"循环系统","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"中枢神经系统","fourth":"骨骼肌肉系统","answerPic":"","first":"免疫系统"}],"basic":"1"},{"ename":"ay","cunt":25,"grade":"1.0","cname":"A1型题/单选题","shiti":[{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"婴幼儿，4个月，早期萌芽，萌了几颗牙齿","discription":"本题考查体格生长常用指标及测量方法。牙齿：人出生后4～10个月乳牙开始萌出，12个月未萌出者为乳牙萌出延迟。约于2岁半乳牙出齐。2岁内乳牙数目为月龄减4～6。6岁左右萌出第l颗恒磨牙，12岁萌出第2颗恒磨牙，17～18岁萌出第3颗恒磨牙(智齿)。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0004_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"4颗","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"6颗","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"10颗","fourth":"8颗","answerPic":"","first":"2颗"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"门脉高压患者出血的特点是","discription":"在门静脉压增高的的状态下，常发生典型的病理生理变化之一是静脉交通支扩张，突出改变是此处门一腔静脉交通支扩张，以食底下段及胃底交通支最为重要，食底下段及胃底曲张静脉突然破裂发生急性大出血，患者会呕吐鲜红色血液或排出柏油样便，甚至很快形成休克；由于肝功能损害至凝血功能障碍，脾功能亢进致血小板减少，因此出血常不易自止。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0012_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"以便血为主，可自行停止","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"有呕血、便血、可自行停止","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"出血量小，可自行停止","fourth":"有呕血、便血、不能自行停止","answerPic":"","first":"以呕血为主，可自行停止"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者女，40岁。孕2产2，行子宫肌瘤切除术后1天。此时应为患者采取的体位是","discription":"半坐位的适用范围：(1)某些面部及颈部手术后，减少局部出血。(2)胸腔疾病、胸部创伤或心脏疾病引起呼吸困难的患者，采取半坐位由于重力原因，部分血液留滞下肢和盆腔，回心血量减少，从而减轻肺淤血和心脏负担；同时使膈肌下降，减少腹腔内脏器对心肺的压力，肺活量增加，有利于气体交换，使呼吸困难的症状得到改善。(3)腹腔、盆腔手术后或者有炎症的患者，采取半坐位可使腹腔渗出液流入盆腔，促使感染局限，便于引流。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0016_201804","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"右侧卧位","subjectTypeEname":"ay","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"去枕平卧位","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"左侧卧位","fourth":"半坐卧位","answerPic":"","first":"中凹位"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"1岁女婴，出生史正常，喂养正常。现进行常规生长发育检查。该女婴的左手腕部X线摄片，可显示的骨化中心数量最多为","discription":"本题考查